---
const features = [
  'Productos Premium',
  'Atencion Personalizada',
  'Ambiente Higienico',
  'Tecnicas Vanguardistas',
];
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-40 bg-white" id="nosotros">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-24 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="about-image aspect-[4/5] bg-gradient-to-br from-stone to-beige relative overflow-hidden reveal">
        <div class="absolute inset-8 border border-gold-light pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-warm-gray">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 mb-4 opacity-40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M20 21V19C20 17.9391 19.5786 16.9217 18.8284 16.1716C18.0783 15.4214 17.0609 15 16 15H8C6.93913 15 5.92172 15.4214 5.17157 16.1716C4.42143 16.9217 4 17.9391 4 19V21"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">Foto del Estudio</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="about-content py-8">
        <p class="section-tag reveal">Sobre Nosotros</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 reveal reveal-delay-1">Queen Studio Art Nails</h2>

        <p class="text-base text-color-text-light leading-relaxed mb-8 reveal reveal-delay-2">
          En Queen Studio creemos que cada mano merece una obra de arte. Nuestro compromiso es ofrecer servicios de nail art de la mas alta calidad, utilizando productos premium y tecnicas innovadoras que marcan tendencia.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base text-color-text-light leading-relaxed mb-8 reveal reveal-delay-2">
          Ubicados en el corazon de Providencia, Antofagasta, hemos creado un espacio donde la elegancia y el cuidado personal se encuentran. Tu satisfaccion es nuestra inspiracion.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-16 reveal reveal-delay-3">
          {features.map((feature) => (
            <div class="about-feature flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-color-text">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <span>{feature}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
